                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Create contests for <strong>Facebook</strong>,  <strong>Twitter</strong> and more</h3><p>Install an application that lets your followers participate.  Easypromos adheres 100% to all social media platform policies and guidelines.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Compatible with all <strong>mobile devices</strong></h3><p>The contest interface has been designed to provide users with an optimum experience when participating via smartphone or tablet.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Combine various types of promotions to create a <strong>tailor-made campaign</strong></h3><p>With Easypromos you can make all of your ideas a reality. With over 200 features, it is the most complete, customizable and flexible platform on the market.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Install a promotion on any <strong>website, blog</strong> or <strong>e-commerce page</strong></h3><p>Use the widgets system to embed the contests you create on any website.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3><strong>Automate</strong> the  promotions process</h3><p>Program mechanical tasks such as: sending emails, distributing coupons and voucher codes, sending alerts and notifications, synchronizing with mailing lists, and so on.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Analyze and measure the <strong>data</strong> and <strong>results</strong> of your contests</h3><p>Segment your database of participants, add them to your Social CRM or mailing lists, and calculate the ROI and impact of your online campaigns.</p></li>
            </ul><ul class="checks column blue large-6">              <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Design and upload <strong>your own design</strong></h3><p>Customize and work on each and every detail of your campaign design. The smallest graphical details can make all the difference.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Includes <strong>30 predefined languages</strong> and supports multi-language promotions  </h3><p>You can create and publish a promotion in multiple languages and you have access to a tool for customizing the predefined translations of each language. </p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>You don’t need <strong>any programming knowledge</strong></h3><p>Create promotions and contests in minutes. You have an intuitive interface which has been designed so that marketing teams don’t have to depend on their IT or programming department.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>We are always ready to support you and offer our <strong>personalized attention</strong></h3><p>You can count on an experienced team that will provide you with 24-hour support, every day of the year, as well as a documentation center with guides, video tutorials and online help.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Generate <strong>viral</strong> contests via <strong>social campaigns</strong></h3><p>Easypromos is integrated with social networks such as Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, Instagram and Google+ to maximize the participation, virality and visibility of your campaigns.</p></li>
                          <li class="knk-check custom_before_text"><h3>Control fraud in your <span>voting contests</span></h3><p>Easypromos includes an antifraud system with 11 security controls to help you detect and prevent bad practices in your voting contests.</p></li>
